<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <style> 
    body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; }
    .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
    .header { color: #2c3e50; border-bottom: 1px solid #eee; padding-bottom: 10px; }
    .footer { margin-top: 20px; font-size: 12px; color: #7f8c8d; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <h1 class="header">Account Activated</h1>
    <p>Dear <%= name %>,</p>
    <p>Your account has been activated by an administrator. You now have full access to our platform.</p>
    <p>If you didn't request this activation, please contact our support team immediately.</p>
    <div class="footer">
      <p>Best regards,<br>Your Application Team</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>